==Introduction==
駆逐艦や海防艦などに装備された両用砲です。<br>
特筆する高い性能を誇るわけではありませんが、対艦、対地、対空、いずれの戦闘も可能なある程度実用的な両用砲として、<br>
後期の小型戦闘艦艇に装備されました。

A dual-purpose gun equipped by destroyers and coastal defence ships.<br>
It didn't boast particularly good performance but it was a dual-purpose gun capable of anti-ship, anti-ground and anti-air combat.<br>
It was equipped on late-war small-sized combat ships.

==Fit Bonuses==
[[Yuubari#Second Upgrade|Yuubari Kai Ni]] receives the following bonus from each gun:
:+1 [[File:Icon_Gun.png]] and +1 [[File:Icon_AA.png]]
If upgraded to at least ★+7, this gun provides bonuses to [[Destroyer Escorts]], [[:Category:Mutsuki_Class|Mutsuki-class]] and [[:Category:Kamikaze_Class|Kamikaze-class]] destroyers, [[Kinu#Second Upgrade|Kinu Kai Ni]], and [[Yura#Second Upgrade|Yura Kai Ni]].

